map_npcs.name: Lost Raider
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Where could the rest of them be?

map_npcs.name: Researcher Jett
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: I guess I've really hit rock-bottom.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
I signed up as part of the team studying this planet's geology.
But my pay's awful, I guess I should've been a little *boulder*.
Hahahaha...ha...
So, wanna rumble?

map_npcs.name: Mr. Nice
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ohoho, hello there traveller, the name's Mr. Nice!
Thank you for freeing me from a potentially gruesome fate!
I never thought a chest in a cave would be my grave!
Now, as for compensation... 
I'd offer you a battle, but I haven't a party of my own quite yet!
I must be on my way, things to see and places to be and whatnot.
Here, take these as means of compensation, toodles my good friend!

map_npcs.name: Rival Cade
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Ugh, not again...
I mean, uh, I meant for it to go like that.
Yep.
Anyway, see ya round. Don't end up like that researcher dude did.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, I hear you're moving up in the world. 
Well don't you worry, so am I.
In fact, why don't I show you?
